card_text: Cannot be Special Summoned. When this card is Normal Summoned: You can target 1 of your banished Level 4 or lower "Blackwing" monsters; Special Summon it in Defense Position. You can banish this card from the GY to activate 1 of the following effects;$N●Place Black Feather Counter(s) on 1 "Black-Winged Dragon" you control, equal to the number of card(s) your opponent controls.$N●Place 1 Wedge Counter on each face-up monster your opponent controls that does not have one.
